{"tid":733361,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[甲組尾班車]蔡思貝 對 林映蔚--2017-18 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽升班附加賽決賽","createTime":"2018-07-07T16:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T17:08:12.000Z","uid":92376,"like":75,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60e03d19df42e9b6120725e64e0d94c8b9a5730c","tid":733361,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蔡思貝v林映蔚<br />\n<br />\n乙組全季積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MryE37s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMryE37s.png&h=37e50aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽升班附加賽決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-7-8 12:30am-10:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5Tq9ROH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5Tq9ROH.png&h=a285c4f3&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cng1C5V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fcng1C5V.png&h=dd5ce60c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(9)蔡思貝vs林映蔚(8)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"dd0e3ccd50f9418823c190a7554e439a69f315b7","tid":733361,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"今場勝方將會升班到18/19甲組女神聯賽"},{"pid":"69ad3b1032b6a6acaa936af8e551d9c